e father’s name (i.e. so-and-so, the son of so-and-so) and beseech Almighty Allah to repel his harm and save from his evils. Most certainly, Almighty Allah will do, if He wills. Then, you may prostrate yourself, submit your request, and beseech Almighty Allah earnestly and purely. Verily, if anyone offers this amaal, the doors of the heavens will be opened and his requests will be granted.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ab apne dushman ka naam uske waalid ke naam ke saath (yaani fulaan ibne fulaan) le kar Allah (s.w.t) se uske sharr se panah maange, Insha-Allah haajat puri hogi. Phir sajdeh mein ja kar Allah (s.w.t) se khuloose dil se iltemaas kare. Yaqeenan, agar koi is amaal ko anjaam de, to Jannat ke darwaaze uske liye khool jaate hai ta-keh uski dua fauran qabool ho.", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "Arabi